YAML is a human readable serialization standard used in conjunction with other programming lanuages to write configuration files. similar to json is designed to be human readable
Playbook contains a list of steps whih the user wants to execute on particular time. 
It is the cor feature of ansible and pushes configuration of waht ansible is to execute.
It runs sequentially. It is a list of to-do action for ansibe
Ansible has it own module library and are standalone reusable script that can be used by the nsible API or by the ansible playbook programs
Ansible modules are reusable standalone scripts that can be used by the asnible api, ansible or ansible-playbook

